I"/<h1 class="no_toc fs-9" id="colours">Colours</h1>

<p class="fs-6 fw-300">When it comes to colours, many websites die in beauty. Often CI colours for print are taken over 1:1 into the web and this does not always work very well for people with impaired vision.</p>

<hr />

