<hr />

<h2 id="it-affects-more-people-than-you-think">It affects more people than you think</h2>

<p>According to <a href="https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/blindness-and-visual-impairment/" title="WHO Blindness and vision impairment report" target="_blank">WHO</a> in 2020 there are 2.2 billion people with impaired vision. Of these, 300 million people are affected by colour blindness in various forms. And for this reason, designers should definitely think about colors and contrasts. <strong>With little effort, the accessibility of a page can be massively improved</strong>.</p>

